'''NGC 1559'''是一個位於[[网罟座|网罟座]]的[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]。該星系同時也是[[西佛星系|西佛星系]]。雖然NGC 1559起初被認為是[[劍魚座星系團|劍魚座星系團]]的成員星系<ref name="Huchraetal1982">{{citation
 | bibcode = 1982ApJ...257..423H
 | title = Groups of galaxies. I - Nearby groups
 | doi = 10.1086/160000
 | date = June 15, 1982
 | journal = Astrophysical Journal
 | issue = Part 1
 | volume = 257
 | pages = 423–437
 | author = Huchra, J. P. | author2 =Geller, M. J.
}}</ref>，稍後的觀測結果卻顯示它並不屬於任一星系團或星系群，甚至沒有臨近伴星系存在<ref name="Becketal2002">{{citation
 | bibcode = 2002A&A...391...83B
 | title = Magnetic fields in barred galaxies. I. The atlas
 | date = August 2002
 | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361:20020642
 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics
 | volume = 391
 | issue = 1
 | pages = 83–102
 | author = Beck, R. |display-authors=4  | author2 =Shoutenkov, V. | author3 =Ehle, M. | author4 =Harnett, J. I. | author5 =Haynes, R. F. | author6 =Shukurov, A. | author7 =Sokoloff, D. D. | author8 =Thierbach, M.
|arxiv = astro-ph/0207201 }}</ref><ref name="Maiaetal1989">{{citation
 | bibcode = 1989ApJS...69..809M
 | date = April 1989
 | journal = Astrophysical Journal Supplement Series
 | issn = 0067-0049
 | volume = 69
 | pages = 809–829
 | doi = 10.1086/191328
 | title = A catalog of southern groups of galaxies
 | author = Maia, M. A. G. | author2 =da Costa, L. N. | author3 =Latham, David W.
}}</ref>。NGC 1559有巨大的螺旋臂結構，以及高[[恆星形成|恆星形成]]率<ref name="Becketal2002" />。該星系有一個接近東西走向，在天球上橫跨40角秒的小型棒狀結構<ref name="Becketal2002" />。它的棒狀結構與盤面是極為強烈的無線電波發射源<ref name="Becketal2002" />。

2005年，天文學家在NGC 1559內發現[[Ia超新星|Ia超新星]][[SN_2005df|SN 2005df]]。該星系內還曾經發現2顆[[超新星|超新星]]SN 1984J和SN 1986L。而這三顆超新星都是由澳大利亞業餘天文學家[[羅伯特·埃文斯_(天文學家)|羅伯特·埃文斯]]發現<ref>{{cite web|title=Supernova Discoveries by Rev. Robert Evans|url=http://revivals.arkangles.com/supernovadiscoveries.php|website=http://revivals.arkangles.com/|accessdate=11 July 2015|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6QJUITxOO?url=http://revivals.arkangles.com/supernovadiscoveries.php|archivedate=2014-06-14|df=}}</ref>。

